<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}} — MeoW</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdf2f8 0%, #fce7f3 50%, #f5f3ff 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 680px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .brand {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .brand h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d946a8, #a855f7);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .brand p {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .alert {
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .alert-error { background: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; color: #991b1b; }
        .alert-success { background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #22c55e; color: #166534; }
        .alert-info { background: #fdf6ff; border-left: 4px solid #d946a8; color: #701a75; }

        .header-section {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .header-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }

        .header-section p {
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .cat-card {
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .cat-photo {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            border: 2px solid #f0abfc;
        }

        .cat-photo-placeholder {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce7f3, #f5f3ff);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            border: 2px solid #f0abfc;
        }

        .cat-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }

        .cat-meta {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        }

        .care-block {
            background: #fdf6ff;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .care-label {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #d946a8;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
        }

        .care-section + .care-section {
            margin-top: 0.6rem;
        }

        .ack-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .ack-section p {
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .btn-ack {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.85rem 2.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d946a8, #a855f7);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
        }

        .btn-ack:hover {
            opacity: 0.92;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .already-acked {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .already-acked .big-check {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .already-acked p {
            color: #166534;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="brand">
            <h1>🐱 MeoW</h1>
            <p>Cat Safety Network</p>
        </div>

        {{#if error}}
            <div class="alert alert-error">{{error}}</div>
        {{else}}
            {{#if acked}}
                <div class="alert alert-success">✅ You've acknowledged — {{ownerName}}'s cats are in good hands!</div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="card">
                <div class="header-section">
                    <h2>🐾 {{ownerName}} needs your help</h2>
                    <p>They've marked themselves as unavailable. Please review the care instructions below and acknowledge that you're looking after their cats.</p>
                </div>

                {{#each cats}}
                <div class="cat-card">
                    {{#if this.photoUrl}}
                        <img class="cat-photo" src="{{this.photoUrl}}" alt="{{this.name}}">
                    {{else}}
                        <div class="cat-photo-placeholder">🐱</div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <div class="cat-info">
                        <h3>{{this.name}}</h3>
                        <div class="cat-meta">{{this.breed}}{{#if this.age}} · {{this.age}} yrs{{/if}}</div>
                        <div class="care-block">
                            {{#if this.careInstructions.feedingSchedule}}
                            <div class="care-section">
                                <span class="care-label">Feeding</span>
                                {{this.careInstructions.feedingSchedule}}
                                {{#if this.careInstructions.foodBrand}} — {{this.careInstructions.foodBrand}}{{/if}}
                            </div>
                            {{/if}}
                            {{#if this.careInstructions.allergies}}
                            <div class="care-section">
                                <span class="care-label">Allergies</span>
                                {{this.careInstructions.allergies}}
                            </div>
                            {{/if}}
                            {{#if this.careInstructions.conditions}}
                            <div class="care-section">
                                <span class="care-label">Conditions</span>
                                {{this.careInstructions.conditions}}
                            </div>
                            {{/if}}
                            {{#if this.careInstructions.medications}}
                            <div class="care-section">
                                <span class="care-label">Medications</span>
                                {{this.careInstructions.medications}}
                            </div>
                            {{/if}}
                            {{#if this.careInstructions.vetName}}
                            <div class="care-section">
                                <span class="care-label">Vet</span>
                                {{this.careInstructions.vetName}}{{#if this.careInstructions.vetPhone}} — {{this.careInstructions.vetPhone}}{{/if}}
                            </div>
                            {{/if}}
                            {{#if this.careInstructions.notes}}
                            <div class="care-section" style="background:#fffbeb;border-left-color:#f59e0b;">
                                <span class="care-label" style="color:#92400e;">Notes</span>
                                {{this.careInstructions.notes}}
                            </div>
                            {{/if}}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}

                {{#if alreadyAcknowledged}}
                    <div class="already-acked">
                        <div class="big-check">✅</div>
                        <p>You already acknowledged this request.</p>
                    </div>
                {{else if acked}}
                    <div class="already-acked">
                        <div class="big-check">✅</div>
                        <p>You're all set! {{ownerName}} has been notified.</p>
                    </div>
                {{else}}
                    <div class="ack-section">
                        <p>By acknowledging, you confirm you're aware of the situation and will look after these cats.</p>
                        <form method="POST" action="/guardian-access/{{token}}/acknowledge">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn-ack">✅ I'm on it — Acknowledge</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
</body>
</html>